com.interpss.dstab.algo

Interface DynamicSimuAlgorithm

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, NetworkRef<BaseDStabNetwork<?,?>>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DynamicSimuAlgorithmImpl

    public interface DynamicSimuAlgorithm
extends NetworkRef<BaseDStabNetwork<?,?>>
    A representation of the model object 'Dynamic Simu Algorithm'. DStab simulation algorithm. It holds parameters for the simulation. The actual implementation is done in the IDStabSolver object.

    The following features are supported:

    • Total Simu Time Sec
    • Simu Step Sec
    • Simu Method
    • Output Filtered
    • Output Var Id List
    • Disable Dynamic Event
    • Ref Machine
    • Aclf Algorithm
    • Simu Output Handler
    • Script Output Handler
    • Dynamic Event Handler
    See Also:
    DstabAlgorithmPackage.getDynamicSimuAlgorithm()
